  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Bihar has three distinct seasons: hot summer (March–June), monsoon (July–September) and cool winter (October–February). October to March is ideal for tourism — skies are clear, the Ganges is serene and all major pilgrimage circuits are fully accessible.</p>
